Package: convertr
Title: Convert Between Quarto, RMarkdown, and R Scripts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Martina", "Sladekova", , "m.sladekova@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5059-6576"))
Description: A package for conversion between Quarto, RMarkdown and R scripts. When converting from Rmd to Qmd, global knitr options are taken from the setup chunk and moved into the YAML. For html documents, the `self-contained: true` option is added. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: 
  dplyr,
  purrr,
  rlang,
  stringr,
  tibble,
  tidyr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
URL: https://github.com/martinasladek/convertr
BugReports: https://github.com/martinasladek/convertr/issues
